393
00:40:55,843 --> 00:41:00,643
Yet you'd drag our entire clan
into conflict with them?

394
00:41:04,362 --> 00:41:10,362
You never should have followed
that Xiao boy into provoking them.

395
00:41:10,362 --> 00:41:12,962
But Master Xiao and Lady Hui Shan
are in grave danger.

396
00:41:12,962 --> 00:41:14,723
