397
00:41:14,723 --> 00:41:17,763
Do you think hiding spares us from trouble?

398
00:41:17,763 --> 00:41:21,962
What if Power Gang invades Qianxi next, Father?

399
00:41:21,962 --> 00:41:27,362
This matter exceeds you juniors' concerns.

400
00:41:27,362 --> 00:41:29,162
Our Hailin Sect

401
00:41:29,882 --> 00:41:34,920
